  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist Bunring Skies</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><br><br>Bighead Runner is an arcade endless runner that challenges you to collect coins and conquer the leaderboards! Dash, jump, and slide through procedurally generated stages, striving to beat your best score and unlock awesome skins. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/863490/extras/36f57415ceb8d3101f39999fa69bfc83.poster.avif?t=1762272972\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/863490/extras/36f57415ceb8d3101f39999fa69bfc83.webm?t=1762272972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/863490/extras/36f57415ceb8d3101f39999fa69bfc83.mp4?t=1762272972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Survive through increasingly dificulty procedurally generated levels.<br></li><li>Addictive coin eater arcade experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/863490/extras/5a112610735c3de20b7002e22c1c66a8.poster.avif?t=1762272972\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/863490/extras/5a112610735c3de20b7002e22c1c66a8.webm?t=1762272972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/863490/extras/5a112610735c3de20b7002e22c1c66a8.mp4?t=1762272972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Get the best score and try to get to the top of the online leaderboards.<br></li><li>Collect coins to unlock new skins.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/863490/extras/2f426f6e4928058eb0b8289859ca57fc.poster.avif?t=1762272972\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/863490/extras/2f426f6e4928058eb0b8289859ca57fc.webm?t=1762272972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/863490/extras/2f426f6e4928058eb0b8289859ca57fc.mp4?t=1762272972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Great to play both with joystick or keyboard.<br></li><li>Oldschool pixel art graphics.<br></li><li>Original soundtrack.</li></ul>",
